text.tspan: Praise of the Lord — His Name
Father God, who calls you through faith in His Word,
Holy Breath, dispensing, now is Jesus the Son,
Jesus is Jehovah, the Great I Am,
Jesus Christ the Savior: perfect, sinless man;
Jesus as the “I Am” is all we need,
On this living person we feed.
The eternal “To Be” who sets us free,
We by faith confessing, Lord, we believe,
Father God, be worshipped and well-pleased.
